# --- Repository hygiene: never commit these (see AGENTS.md "Repository hygiene") ---
# Dependency dirs anywhere in the tree (npm/pnpm). A committed node_modules
# (112MB rollup binary) once blocked the Codeberg->GitHub mirror.
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
docs/node_modules.bak/
